<p>March 22nd, 7-8:30PM</p>
<p>Location: Romney 172</p>
<p>Admission: Free</p>
<p>Film Submission: Free</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Come together with other ski and snowboard enthusiasts to watch footage from this winter's ski season.<span style="white-space: pre;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Create a ski/snowboard film to be viewed by an audience on March 22nd.  All submissions must be made by March 19th to the Activities Office (MC 101) front desk in DVD form.  Submissions must be no longer than 8 minutes.   Submit DVD's with contact name and phone number.  Submissions will only be accepted from BYU-Idaho students and employees.  Music and content must be university approved.  Any crude, vulgar, or immodest content will not be shown in the festival.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="Semesters" label="Available Semesters" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><AvailableFall type="boolean" label="Available Fall" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</AvailableFall><AvailableWinter type="boolean" label="Available Winter" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">true</AvailableWinter><AvailableSpring type="boolean" label="Available Spring" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</AvailableSpring><AvailableSummer type="boolean" label="Available Summer" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</AvailableSummer><xPower Type="List" List="Date" Name="DateElements" label="Dates" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" display="localdateshort" Expanded="true"><Date type="date" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" display="localdateshort" Expanded="false" UTC="true">20120322T18:00:00</Date></xPower><AdditionalInformation type="dhtml" label="Additional Information" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>For more information please contact...</p>
